# Diagram Agent — Project Reference

Complete requirements to rebuild this project from scratch.

---

## Purpose

An AI agent that generates diagrams from natural language and optional images. The user describes what they want in text and optionally attaches an image (screenshot, photo, hand-drawn sketch). The agent produces one of three output formats and saves the result to MongoDB.

**Supported output formats:**
- `drawio` — complete importable `<mxfile>` XML (draw.io / VS Code drawio extension)
- `mermaid_sequence` — Mermaid `sequenceDiagram` code
- `mermaid_flowchart` — Mermaid `flowchart TD/LR` code

**Two interfaces:**
1. `adk web` — browser dev UI for interactive testing (supports image upload)
2. REST API — fire-and-forget HTTP service for other systems to call

