## Session State Contract

Keys written during an agent run. Both agent and API layer read from these.

| Key | Written by | Read by | Value |
|---|---|---|---|
| `image_summary` | `image_extractor` (via `output_key`) | coordinator prompt, generator writer prompts | Structured text description of the image |
| `requested_format` | `runner.py` (initial state) | coordinator prompt | `"drawio"` \| `"mermaid_sequence"` \| `"mermaid_flowchart"` \| `None` |
| `diagram_code` | Each writer LlmAgent (via `output_key`) | `DiagramValidator`, `runner.py` | Raw diagram code string (latest attempt) |
| `validation_feedback` | `DiagramValidator` on failure | Writer LlmAgent prompt (`{validation_feedback?}`) | `list[str]` of error messages |
| `final_format` | `DiagramValidator` on success | `runner.py` | The format that passed validation |
| `diagram_title` | *(optional, unused currently)* | `runner.py` uses `text[:120]` as title instead | — |

