## Running the Project

### Prerequisites
```
uv sync                              # installs all dependencies
mongosh --eval "db.runCommand({ping:1})"   # confirm MongoDB is running
gcloud auth application-default login      # Vertex AI ADC (already configured)
```
Edit `diagram_agent/.env` and set `GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT` to your real project ID.

### Dev UI (adk web)
```
adk web
```
Open browser → select `diagram_coordinator`. Supports image upload directly in the chat.

### REST API
```
uvicorn diagram_agent.api.server:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
```
Swagger UI: `http://localhost:8000/docs`

### Validation smoke tests
```
python test_validation.py
```
Expected: `15 / 15 tests passed.`

